A data source is accessed via a specia kind of resource known as a data resource, declared using a data block

Example:
data "aws_instance" "foo" {}

Folowing this terraform reads from "aws_instance" and export the result under the given local name "foo"

With filter:

data "aws_instance" "foo" {
    filter {
        name = "tag:Team"
        value = ["Production"]
    }
}

